uk.gov.gchq.palisade.data.service.reader

Class SimpleDataReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.data.service.reader.SerialisedDataReader
      • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.data.service.reader.SimpleDataReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataReader
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExampleSimpleDataReader

    public class SimpleDataReader
extends SerialisedDataReader

    The SimpleDataReader is a *very* simple implementation of DataReader that just maintains a Map of Resource to List of raw data, allowing you to add and retrieve resources.

    It should only be used for examples/demos.
